OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 22 May to Sun 31 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure is expected to bring a
OL,7,Fgood deal of fair, warm weather to the
OL,8,FUK during the Bank Holiday weekend. It
OL,9,Fmay be cloudier with a chance of some
OL,10,Fshowers across Northern Ireland and
OL,11,FScotland, but even here it will be
OL,12,Fmuch warmer than the previous week and
OL,13,Fthere will be plenty of dry weather
OL,14,Faround too. Through the following
OL,15,Fweek, high pressure is expected to
OL,16,Fbroadly remain in place for much of
OL,17,Fthe UK, and fine weather is likely to
OL,18,Fcontinue for most of the country.
OL,19,FThere may be occasions where low
OL,20,Fpressure to the north may bring some
OL,21,Fbrief spells of rain across northern
OL,22,Fparts, but in general fair weather
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fwill dominate. Temperatures are
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fexpected to be above normal, feeling
OL,25,Fvery warm at times with light winds.
